f the answer is yes, then ask us about a low-dose CT lung cancer screening. <a href="http://www.stpaulradiology.com/services/ancillary/lung-screening">LEARN MORE.</a>";}}s:9:"amenities";a:6:{i:0;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:54:"/assets/img/icons/Reduced Radiation-20151015113449.png";s:7:"amenity";s:17:"Reduced Radiation";s:11:"description";s:58:"Our Intego PET infusion systems reduce radiation exposure.";}i:1;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:38:"/assets/img/icons/Same-Day Service.png";s:7:"amenity";s:16:"Same-Day Service";s:11:"description";s:47:"Including convenient weekend and evening hours.";}i:2;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:48:"/assets/img/icons/Complimentary taxi service.png";s:7:"amenity";s:26:"Complimentary Taxi Service";s:11:"description";s:54:"For those who require transportation to our locations.";}i:3;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:51:"/assets/img/icons/Outpatient Conscious Sedation.png";s:7:"amenity";s:29:"Outpatient Conscious Sedation";s:11:"description";s:38:"For patients who need deeper sedation.";}i:4;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:34:"/assets/img/icons/Cinemavision.png";s:7:"amenity";s:12:"CinemaVision";s:11:"description";s:54:"A peaceful distraction for patients needing MRI Exams.";}i:5;a:3:{s:4:"icon";s:34:"/assets/img/icons/Free Parking.png";s:7:"amenity";s:12:"Free Parking";s:11:"description";s:52:"Safe and convenient at all of our imaging locations.";}}s:16:"team_description";s:339:"St. Paul Radiology is a group of 70 independent physicians who rank among Minnesota’s top board-certified, fellowship-trained, subspecialty imaging experts. In addition, our experienced nurses, technicians and administrative staff are courteous, efficient and available to answer any questions you may have about the services we provide.";s:12:"testimonials";a:8:{i:0;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:8:"Linda H.";s:8:"location";s:16:"October 27, 2012";s:5:"photo";s:29:"/assets/img/avatars/Linda.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:273:"I came here for an ultrasound and everything from the parking to obtaining a copy of my films and report went as smooth as silk. Everything seemed to be very organized and efficient. My US appointment was right on time, and the US tech was highly professional and pleasant.";}i:1;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:10:"Cortney G.";s:8:"location";s:12:"June 7, 2011";s:5:"photo";s:31:"/assets/img/avatars/Cortney.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:153:"Quick service, nice and professional staff. St. Paul Radiology makes an MRI a comfortable, simple experience, which is much appreciated by this busy gal!";}i:2;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:16:"December 4, 2012";s:5:"photo";s:33:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:100:"The entire staff was very welcoming, my procedure was fully explained. I had a wonderful experience.";}i:3;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:17:"December 22, 2012";s:5:"photo";s:48:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous-20151020125349.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:235:"I went to the Roseville Clinic on Co. Rd D and Cleveland Ave. My nurse who did the exam was gentle, informative and very friendly as was the staff. I have always appreciated the care and professional quality given to each of my visits.";}i:4;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:16:"January 14, 2013";s:5:"photo";s:48:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous-20151020125846.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:145:"I was at Gallery and the lady that helped me was most wonderful. It is nice dealing with a genuine and real person that cares about your comfort.";}i:5;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:15:"January 8, 2013";s:5:"photo";s:48:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous-20151020125915.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:133:"Joyce who did my exam was wonderful. She made me very comfortable and answered all my questions. Dr. Goertzen was very pleasant also.";}i:6;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:16:"January 11, 2012";s:5:"photo";s:48:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous-20151020125946.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:141:"Felt very comfortable for the needle injections which didn't even hurt me & such nice nurses & Dr. Goertzen was very nice & I trusted in him!";}i:7;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Anonymous";s:8:"location";s:16:"January 15, 2012";s:5:"photo";s:48:"/assets/img/avatars/Anonymous-20151020130037.jpg";s:11:"testimonial";s:201:"The woman conducting my Mammogram was as gentle and caring as can be. I've had her for the last three times and seeing her familiar and friendly face made the whole experience so much more comfortable.";}}s:22:"mobile_app_description";s:213:"At St. Paul Radiology, we offer a Mobile App with convenient links and resources all in one place, so that our referring physicians and their staff can stay connected and informed about our practices and services.";s:19:"mobile_app_features";a:5:{i:0;a:1:{s:7:"feature";s:33:"Speak with a Radiologist by Phone";}i:1;a:1:{s:7:"feature";s:22:"Scheduling Information";}i:2;a:1:{s:7:"feature";s:45:"Imaging Centers Location Information and Maps";}i:3;a:1:{s:7:"feature";s:48:"Reports and Images via our Physicians Web Portal";}i:4;a:1:{s:7:"feature";s:27:"General Contact Information";}}s:15:"mobile_app_link";s:62:"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/st.-paul-radiology/id468653363";s:24:"mobile_app_download_info";s:100:"The St. Paul Radiology Mobile App is available for download from the Apple App Store on your iPhone.";s:17:"featured_services";a:4:{i:0;s:34:"/services/ancillary/lung-screening";i:1;s:35:"/services/ancillary/heart-screening";i:2;s:35:"/services/ancillary/colon-screening";i:3;s:36:"/services/ancillary/breast-screening";}s:24:"featured_teammates_label";s:19:"Featured Physicians";s:24:"testimonials_description";s:377:"St. Paul Radiology is dedicated to the safe and efficient use of advanced imaging and other radiology services to help improve the health of the patients we serve. We know we provide some of the best services in Minnesota, and our patients agree. Click  <a href="http://http://stpaulradiology.com/about/our-patients-speak">here</a> to see more patient reviews and testimonials.";s:32:"refer_a_pat